name: 2023 The 6th International Conference on Computational Intelligence and Intelligent Systems
content: Publication: Conference proceedings will include the accepted and registered full papers by ACM CONFERENCE PROCEEDINGS with ISBN 978-1-4503-9762-9, which is indexed by Ei Compendex and Scopus. CIIS conference proceedings for last 5 years have been successfully indexed by Ei Compendex and Scopus three months after conference.
